  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0da2\u0db1\u0dba \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The station master calls off the strike",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kasun Chamara, Secretary of the Railway Station Master's Union, said that the 24-hour strike that was scheduled to be implemented from midnight today (5) has been suspended.",
        "Mr. Kasun Chamara further said that as a result of an emergency discussion held with the Union, the Railway Control Authority decided to suspend the strike and accordingly, they will continue to run trains as much as possible for the benefit of the passengers."
      ],
